<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Mikella now has a passive: Compound Interest (Passive)</b></li><ul><li> Mikella's attacks and abilities apply marks of Compound Interest for 2 seconds. The fourth consecutive attack or ability against the same target will consume the marks to deal between 20-100 (+30% Power), based on level.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Waltz (E)</b></li><ul><li> Updated the tool-tip on this ability to reflect the fact that it cannot be used to dash over terrain.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32.1 (July 17th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Gold Standard (W)</b></li><ul><li>Mikella's basic attack will now become immediately able to fire upon triggering this ability.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 29 (May 5th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Final Payment (R)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a visual bug where this ability was invisible if Mikella was offscreen.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Collateral (Q)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 825, from previous value of 930.</li></ul><li>Waltz (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 400, from previous value of 425.</li></ul><li>Final Payment (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 1900, from previous value of 2100.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 18 (November 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Final Payment (R)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ultimate ability has been reduced to 270/480/690, down from 300/510/720.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ultimate ability had been reduced to 1.1, down from 1.2</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 17 (November 7, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Collateral (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The power ratio on this ability has been reduced to 0.4, down from 0.5.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Base Movement Speed reduced to 370, down from 385.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 5 (July 18, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Final Payment (R)</B></li><ul><li>The power ratio on this ability has been reduced to 1.2 per point of power, down from 1.38.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 1 (June 06, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Collateral (Q)</B><ul><li>Fixed a bug where Collateral would sometimes trigger 3 damage events instead of 2 if it hit a target at maximum range.</li></ul></li></ul>